Refuge is a lowkey worship night held every Wednesday evening at the Alpha Gamma Omega house located at 310 Parkway Circle (Opposite side of Bike Tunnel from Segundo). Come on and hangout from 9:45pm10:00pm, Followed by Worship from 10:00pm till about 11:00pm, then you are free to hangout or leave. Take a break from your Study Cages studies, bring your guitars and singing voices, and enjoy some quality hot chocolate and baked goods with Alpha Gamma Omega AGO, Alpha Delta Chi ADX, College Life (Organization) College Life, and others! Come for 10 minutes or stay the whole hour!

